  "body": "To close this issue, we need to implement the epoch transition function for beacon chain node. The epoch transition function affects both crystallized state and the active state. It focuses on the functionalities of:\r\n\r\n- maintaining validator set (which validators got added or removed)\r\n- adjusting balances\r\n- tracking which epoch is last justified and last finalized\r\n- setting FFG check points\r\n\r\nFor every epoch, the node uses the random block hash to shuffle and select shard committees for proposers and attesters selection.",
